title: 209: Who Will Win the Best Division in Football?
itunes:title: 209: Who Will Win the Best Division in Football?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks debate who will come out on top in the loaded AFC West. The guys also ask which teams need to go to the bullpen and pull a current starter for a more talented backup. DJ and Bucky then tell you which defenders they are excited to watch this weekend before they make their college football picks.
